p: As mentioned above, we have identified nine potential natural product inhibitors of cathepsin L by computational screening of 14,011 phytochemicals produced by Indian medicinal plants, and these compounds labelled C1â€“C9 are listed in Supplementary Table S2 along with their PubChem identifier, common name, IUPAC name and structure in SMILES format.
